                  ARP-SH1 GENERAL COMMANDS MANUAL

NAME
    edit - basic file editor

SYNOPSIS
    edit [file]

DESCRIPTION
    The `edit` command allows you to edit a file.

KEY BINDINGS
    ESCAPE      - Save the file and exit
    UP ARROW    - Move up a line
    DOWN ARROW  - Move down a line
    LEFT ARROW  - Move a character to the left
    RIGTH ARROW - Move a character to the right